{"tid":1003682,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【人類已死】蘋果降價策略見效，天貓、蘇寧半月銷量增8成！","createTime":"2019-02-01T00:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T07:44:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"88471782f1c80a06e1193cacb931c94759e8decd","tid":1003682,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Internet1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FInternet1.jpg&h=3de3ff7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據中國傳媒報道，天貓於1月13日起進行iPhone降價促銷以來，截至1月29日，在兩周的時間確實刺激了iPhone銷量，提升了足足76%之多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Internet310.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FInternet310.jpg&h=97a75fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，中國商業零售企業蘇寧易購也表示自1月11日起宣布iPhone降價開始，其蘋果的銷量也爆增，直至1月30日止銷量增長83%。<br />\n<br />\nInternet3<br />\nPhoto from Internet<br />\n<br />\n在此之前，蘋果於大中華地區的銷量表現不佳，導致營收下滑。蘋果CEO庫克也在近日表示考慮在美國以外地區重新思考如何定價。此外，在2019年，蘋果中國也開始在各方面調低售價，像是補貼電商、營運商等，還有通過天貓旗艦店官方渠道發優惠券。"},{"pid":"eeb10e1f871ceeab168d48ed4f067a4373ca53ac","tid":1003682,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0534a07e193effa4efa6e75de32c3e52cb8d07f","tid":1003682,"uid":88029,"like":30,"dislike":11,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:06:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f14e7474d7728d7956be8f88015450df0ffee82","tid":1003682,"uid":41543,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:11:49.000Z","msg":"唔係只買華為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/